Dolores Mantez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dolores_Mantez 0 Dolores Brenda Harding (née Mantey; 17 October 1936 – 30 November 2012), known professionally as Dolores Mantez, was a British television actress of the 1960s and early 1970s, best known for her appearances in Gerry Anderson's science-fiction TV series UFO.
